{"title":"故乡水  咏白天鹅宾馆大厅","authors":["谢韬"],"dates":[{"year":1984,"month":11,"day":6}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"故乡水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咏白天鹅宾馆大厅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谢韬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去岁参观广州白天鹅宾馆，黄辛白、黄其江二同志同游，嘱题“故乡水”大厅，以其布局高雅，独具匠心，不趋西风末流，保持我民族风格与特色。归来，仓促命笔，未及遐思。写景记实，难绘情深，海外侨胞，可共鸣乎？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天鹅立江滨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洁白耸崇楼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"布陈绝精巧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妙趣静中柔。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恍临水帘洞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞瀑落泉幽。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"濯月亭如画，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悬岩壁鸣篌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梦饮故乡水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"客恋古神州。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"游子去异域，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泪洒珠江头。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万缕千丝系，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凭舟几回眸。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寄人篱下久，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旧地复重游。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲友常萦牵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千虑渡春秋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万里归帆远，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一返解百愁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乡水乡情寓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"故居故人留。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海外思乡客，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来此顿忘忧。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南岭山川秀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"景物望中收。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天涯归来意，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国正风流。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}